### ğŸ“ Project Overview

This project implements a **time series forecasting model** using **SARIMA with exogenous variables** (SARIMAX) to predict daily customer connection volumes in a contact center operation.

### âœ… Main Features

- Input data is daily connection logs
- Outlier treatment using quantile clipping
- Day-of-week dummy variables for exogenous signal
- Time series decomposition (trend, seasonality)
- ADF test, ACF and PACF plots for stationarity checks
- Holt-Winters smoothing for comparison
- SARIMA model tuning and forecasting
- Projections plotted vs. last 3 months of real data

---

### âš™ï¸ Technologies Used

- Python 3.10+
- pandas, matplotlib, statsmodels, pmdarima
- Holt-Winters Smoothing (Holt)
- SARIMAX from statsmodels
- Visual outputs with matplotlib

